These are Puzzles for 3x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-1::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: zinnia, azalea, sunflower
There are 3 different nationalities: indian, thai, turkish
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, january, december
1. the person who's birthday is in december is in an even position##4
2. the thai is on the left of the indian##1
3. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
4. the thai is in an even position##4
5. the person who growssunflower is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3     |
| Flower   | sunflower       | zinnia     | azalea    |
| Nationality   | turkish   | thai          | indian   |
| Birthday         | october | december | january |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-2::.
There 3 different types of food: avocado, cabbage, nectarine
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, dubstep, salsa
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, turtle, hamster
1. the owner of the hamster is the person eating nectarine##1
2. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
3. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1
4. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
5. the owner of the hamster is in an even position##4
6. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the fan of salsa##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Food    | avocado     | nectarine  | cabbage  |
| Music-Genre   | salsa | dubstep | funk    |
| Pet     | hedgehog      | hamster    | turtle |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, iced-tea, lemonade
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, american, french
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, skiing, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person drinking juice##1
3. the french is on the right of the canadian##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the french##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |
| Beverage          | juice         | lemonade     | iced-tea   |
| Nationality   | american       | canadian     | french |
| Sport         | weightlifting | lacrosse | skiing |

