.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-4::.
City: miami, liverpool, nizza
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, jet-ski, bike
3 different pets are kept: ferret, goldfish, snake
1. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
3. the person driving the roller is in an odd position##4
4. the person traveling to miami is on the far left##1
5. the person driving the bike is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2     |       3       |
| City   | miami | nizza  | liverpool |
| Transport        | bike | jet-ski  | roller |
| Pet        | ferret | goldfish | snake         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-5::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, february, march
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, jet-ski, motorbike
3 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, mouse
1. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3
2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
4. the owner of the bird is in an odd position##4
5. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far left##1
6. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |
| Birthday   | march | october  | february  |
| Transport   | jet-ski  | bike | motorbike |
| Pet           | chinchilla  | mouse    | bird    |

