.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-6::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, milk, sprite
House: palace, townhouse, gothic-revival
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: house, electronic, country
1. the person drinking cola is between the fan of country and the gothic-revival house##2
2. the palace house is the person drinking milk##1
3. the person drinking cola is on the left of the palace house##1
4. the fan of electronic is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2   |      3      |
| Beverage    | sprite  | cola  | milk        |
| House       | gothic-revival | townhouse | palace |
| Music-Genre   | house    | electronic   | country   |

