.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-7::.
House: modern, gothic-revival, wooden
City: boston, prague, liverpool
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: golf, skateboarding, tennis
1. the gothic-revival house is between the person traveling to boston and the wooden house##2
2. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is in an even position##4
4. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |    3    |
| House   | modern | gothic-revival        | wooden |
| City           | boston   | prague      | liverpool     |
| Sport         | tennis | skateboarding | golf    |

