.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-8::.
3 different games are played: whist, scrabble, go
The people have 3 different jobs:  musician, photographer, pilot
There are 3 different favourite colors: amber, blood-red, ebony
1. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person playing whist##1
2. the person who likes amber is between the pilot and the person playing go##2
3. the photographer is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
4. the person playing go is in an odd position##4
5. the person who likes ebony is the person playing go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2     |      3       |
| Game    | whist   | scrabble | go       |
| Job     | pilot  | musician  | photographer |
| Color   | blood-red | amber  | ebony       |

