.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-9::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: red, azure, coral
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: soul, punk, folk
3 different pets are kept: goat, rabbit, rat
1. the person who likes red is on the right of the person who likes azure##1
2. the fan of soul is in an odd position##4
3. the fan of punk is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
4. the fan of soul is on the right of the fan of punk##1
5. the person who likes red is between the owner of the goat and the person who likes azure##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |       3       |
| Color         | azure | red | coral |
| Music-Genre   | folk       | punk  | soul     |
| Pet           | rabbit     | rat     | goat          |

