.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-10::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: rock-climbing, chess, drawing
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, martial-arts, time-travel
House: wooden, craftsman, tower
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far right##1
2. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
3. the wooden house is on the left or right of the tower house##3
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
5. the tower house is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
6. the person watching time-travel movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |    3    |
| Hobby           | drawing | rock-climbing        | chess   |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | time-travel | epic    |
| House   | tower         | wooden      | craftsman |

