.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-11::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  dancer, pilot, videographer
3 different games are played: snooker, domino, scrabble
There 3 different types of food: asparagus, kale, cauliflower
1. the videographer is the person playing snooker##1
2. the dancer is in an odd position##4
3. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person eating kale##1
4. the pilot is on the left of the dancer##1
5. the person eating asparagus is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2      |    3    |
| Job         | videographer | pilot      | dancer  |
| Game         | snooker         | scrabble      | domino    |
| Food   | asparagus         | cauliflower | kale |

