.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-12::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, mirinda, water
3 different games are played: bridge, backgammon, snooker
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: family, fantasy, time-travel
1. the person playing backgammon is the person drinking water##1
2. the person playing bridge is in an even position##4
3. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
4. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left##1
5. the person playing snooker is the person watching fantasy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |      3       |
| Beverage         | mirinda        | milk  | water      |
| Game           | snooker | bridge | backgammon |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy        | family   | time-travel  |

