1. the person driving the boat is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the tower house##3
3. the fan of rock is in an even position##4
4. the cape-cod house is on the left of the fan of rock##1
5. the person driving the tram is on the right of the fan of blues##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |       2       |     3      |
| Music-Genre    | blues        | rock | punk     |
| House       | cape-cod | tower          | gothic-revival |
| Transport   | subway     | tram          | boat       |

