1. the british is on the left of the french##1
2. the fan of punk is the person who's hobby is baking##1
3. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
4. the british is the fan of r&b##1
5. the french is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |   3    |
