.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-16::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, cooking, hiking
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, lemonade, soy-milk
There 3 different types of food: cranberry, blueberry, pepper
1. the person eating pepper is the person eating pepper##1
2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left or right of the person eating pepper##3
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
4. the person eating blueberry is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
5. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
6. the person who's hobby is hiking is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |
| Hobby         | cooking   | camping     | hiking   |
| Beverage           | lemonade  | sprite | soy-milk |
| Food   | pepper | blueberry     | cranberry |

