.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-17::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: november, may, march
The people use 3 different means of transport: taxi, quad-bike, tram
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, volleyball, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the far left##1
2. the person who's birthday is in november is in an even position##4
3. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
4. the person who's birthday is in may is the person driving the quad-bike##1
5. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| Birthday     | may      | november | march |
| Transport     | quad-bike | taxi      | tram           |
| Sport   | water-polo | climbing  | volleyball    |

