There are 3 different nationalities: russian, french, polish
3 different games are played: monopoly, domino, go
1. the person drinking tea is on the left of the polish##1
2. the person playing monopoly is on the left or right of the person playing go##3
3. the polish is in an odd position##4
4. the russian is on the right of the person playing domino##1
5. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
6. the russian is on the left or right of the person playing monopoly##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |
| Beverage    | mirinda | tea      | sprite     |
| Nationality         | french  | russian | polish        |
| Game   | domino | go    | monopoly |

