.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-20::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: snowboarding, skateboarding, sailing
There 3 different types of food: pepper, watermelon, cranberry
3 different pets are kept: cat, fish, lizard
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the person eating watermelon##2
2. the owner of the lizard is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the lizard is in an odd position##4
4. the person eating cranberry is the owner of the fish##1
5. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
6. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3
7. the person eating pepper is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |     3      |
| Sport         | sailing      | skateboarding | snowboarding |
| Food   | watermelon | pepper      | cranberry    |
| Pet           | lizard      | cat        | fish       |

 